data.description: GREAT NEWS:  Seller offering $7000 towards buyer closing cost or buydown!  Are you looking for your first home and love the outdoors? This home is perfect and just minutes from the entrance of Crowders Mountain State Park. Enjoy this cute all brick ranch with a large screen porch, towering trees and a huge workshop/garage and full privacy fence in the backyard or spend the day hiking Crowders Mountain with your dog! Nature is calling and you will love it. Hardwood floors throughout the home and a cute gas burning woodstove for cozy evenings at home. A center island in the kitchen makes a great gathering spot for entertaining. Three bedrooms and a common bathroom are all tucked down the hall for privacy from your living area.
